<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="grow-vi">grow <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɡrəʊ/    美 /ɡroʊ/  </p>
<p>(grew, grown)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>生长；成长：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Rice grows in warm climates.
水稻在温暖的气候下生长。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I've decided to let my hair grow.
我已决定留长发。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The population of this city is growing every year.
这个城市的人口每年都在增加。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>增长；增加：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My uncle hopes that his business will grow steadily.
我叔叔希望他的生意稳固发展。</p><footer>2016 全国改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The population of this city is growing every year.
这个城市的人口每年都在增加。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>[用作系动词] 逐渐变得；成为：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Truth never grows old.
真理永不过时。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Another 15 minutes passed and I grew bored.
又过去了15分钟，我开始变得不耐烦了。</p><footer>2017 天津</footer></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>逐渐形成；产生：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm sure you will <strong>grow to like</strong> her in time.
我肯定你慢慢就会喜欢她了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The best friendships are the ones that grow naturally.
自然形成的友谊才是最好的。</p><footer>2012 辽宁</footer></div></div>